Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Attractive rent on the CBD’s doorstep

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
201 Leichhardt Street is one of the most prominent commercial buildings in the heart of Brisbane's city fringe suburb of Spring Hill. Intersecting Leichhardt and Wharf St, tenants are within easy walking distance to the CBD, and have access to all modes of public transport including Central Station.

Overall the building has undergone major upgrades which include a complete new entry and lobby providing a stylish and impressive entrance, modernisation of the building lifts and their electronics, as well as new end of trip facilities in the basement.

Key Features:
   -   87-208sqm quality tenancies
   -   Fitted office space
   -   Great natural light
   -   Refurbished entry, lobby, lifts and End of Trip facilities
   -   Easy access to public transport and surrounding retail amenity
   -   Prominent position in evolving upper CBD precinct

For more information or to arrange an inspection, contact the Exclusive Agents.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: FITTED OFFICE SPACE, READY TO GO – OWNER INCENTIVES ON OFFER

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
66 Bowen Street has recently undergone a significant refurbishment which offers two high-quality offices within walking distance of the CBD. 

Located just off Turbot Street, tenants are on the doorstep of the CBD with onsite reserved car parking and easy access to all modes of public transport.

One of the only new spec fit out options available in Spring Hill, 66 Bowen Street is ready now to move in and enjoy the benefits.
The major upgrades include a complete new entry and lobby providing a stylish and impressive entrance, new and building services, LED lighting, modernisation of the building facade and revitalising the balcony breakout area.

Key Features:
•	Up to 338sqm 
•	New spec fit out offering
•	Great natural light 
•	Disabled access
•	Carparking available (1 per 25sqm)
•	Refurbished entry, lobby, façade & balcony area 
•	Easy access to public transport and surrounding retail amenity
•	Prominent position in evolving Upper CBD Precinct

For more information or to arrange an inspection, please contact the CBRE Agents listed.
